TopicTitle: STS 118: Sending a Probe to Jool w/ CoolRockets and Pimp My Kerbals

Articles.Content:
The Eighteenth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Fourteenth Flight of the Tenacious! STS 118's objectives are to deploy the Jool System Probe, return to the KSC runway, and tour the inner Jool system before splashing down on Laythe!

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing, while some is at 8x.

STS 119 Will be the first in a three-part manned Duna series.
